{"tid":717193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】《南早》引消息指中國不向在華美資開刀　憂全部撤離","createTime":"2018-06-25T23:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T00:26:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2118256e3cdd0baf86fb78363b9cc55f52e891d5","tid":717193,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:41:21.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】《南早》引消息指中國不向在華美資開刀　憂全部撤離<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/252847/%e3%80%90%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e3%80%91%e3%80%8a%e5%8d%97%e6%97%a9%e3%80%8b%e5%bc%95%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%91%e5%9c%a8%e8%8f%af%e7%be%8e%e8%b3%87%e9%96%8b/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F252847%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%25b2%25bf%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%2588%25b0%25e3%2580%2591%25e3%2580%258a%25e5%258d%2597%25e6%2597%25a9%25e3%2580%258b%25e5%25bc%2595%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%2581%25af%25e6%258c%2587%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%2590%2591%25e5%259c%25a8%25e8%258f%25af%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%25b3%2587%25e9%2596%258b%2F&d=o9XKG3P0Bsj9OL4NoDYbjWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=94dfdbf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/252847/%e3%80%90%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e3%80%91%e3%80%8a%e5%8d%97%e6%97%a9%e3%80%8b%e5%bc%95%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%91%e5%9c%a8%e8%8f%af%e7%be%8e%e8%b3%87%e9%96%8b/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前警告，中國如果再向美國商品加徵關稅，會再對價值2,000億美元的中國商品加徵關稅作報復，中方則在上周首次提出，會以「質量型」還擊。不過《南華早報》引述消息指，中方已向在華外資派定心丸，稱不會向他們開刀。<br />\n<br />\n《南早》引述消息指，中國國家主席習近平上周四（21日）與一些外資高層舉行圓桌會議，包括UPS 運輸的David Abney、輝瑞藥業的Albert Bourla、凱悅酒店的Thomas Pritzker，以及高盛的David Solomon。習近平向他們重申，中國的市場會保持開放，並清楚表明歡迎美國的企業。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息指，把在華美資企業列作貿易戰其中一部份，並不在中方考慮之列，是因為中國更憂慮外資會因此離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">對於前中國美國商會主席James Zimmerman稱，中國或採更不擇手段及毀滅性的方法對付貿易戰，如指示中國公司及消費不買美國等。不過另一名消息人士就向《南早》稱，中國正努力為貿易戰降溫，這做法並不在中方考慮之列。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亮劍呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbfacf00ad82815bec8fea05514a314449061d4","tid":717193,"uid":98289,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"做乜要為貿易戰降溫呀<br />\n說好的中國不怕打貿易戰呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c38e60eb92768d4cbbef21a47121882b1b388bf","tid":717193,"uid":18569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5dbfacf00ad82815bec8fea05514a314449061d4","tid":717193,"uid":98289,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"做乜要為貿易戰降溫呀<br />\n說好的中國不怕打貿易戰呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:51:51.000Z","msg":"因為中國冇牌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d224a7d84537e28a0014a31d14d71ddfcf12ca","tid":717193,"uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"鄰國真係底褲都輸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/yellow.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd231ce745dd54cdd3279e8e6ae10d9b5a005065","tid":717193,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:54:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3420276bbdf0cf78803f74e5492cf1fbe003b98","tid":717193,"uid":29874,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:56:26.000Z","msg":"叫撚左你支那唔好成日駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家出事啦，把劍呢"},{"pid":"fe1a76224aa9a9316df7d493c20bab78de60154f","tid":717193,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:56:33.000Z","msg":"但香港價照加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7cff09711cdc4cb76062a73cbcb00747c24f54","tid":717193,"uid":25787,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:57:41.000Z","msg"